1
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:09,539
Don't move.

2
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,560
It's fine.

3
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,160
You drive.

4
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,100
I'll pick it up.

5
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,000
Oh no.

6
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,860
My ID card is in the wallet.

7
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,280
If Ziqing finds out,

8
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,840
my fake identity as Gu Haoran

9
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,440
will be completely exposed.

10
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,770
Why are you here?

11
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:36,880
Hello,

12
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:37,640
Ms. Chen.

13
00:01:38,360 --> 00:01:38,960
Luo Xin.

14
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:40,680
Young Master.

15
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:42,840
I said I'd pick you up at 5:00 PM today.

16
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,320
Since you hadn't come back,

17
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,850
I took a nap in the back seat.

18
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:46,759
Really?

19
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,250
Why didn't I notice?

20
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:50,000
The chairman asked me to remind you

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,330
that at 6:00 PM tonight,

22
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,900
you have a business dinner

23
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,000
with Hongtian Group's representatives.

24
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,330
Okay.

25
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:56,200
Got it.

26
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,280
Haoran.

27
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,600
I can get off up ahead.

28
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,120
Haoran.

29
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,000
Why is she suddenly calling me so affectionately?

30
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,460
Ms. Chen's attitude towards my young master

31
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,400
has never been so gentle.

32
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,560
It's fine.

33
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,680
Let me take you back.

34
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,160
No need.

35
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:19,200
It's more important for you to go to the banquet.

36
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,930
And my driver will be here soon.

37
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,480
All right.

38
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:29,010
Then be careful.

39
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,000
Haoran, let's meet up next time.

40
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,440
Bye.

41
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,320
Bye.

42
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,690
Take care, Ms. Chen.

43
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,200
When did you get here?

44
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,970
Give it to me.

45
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,480
You are too careless.

46
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,080
If it weren't for me just now,

47
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,680
you would have been exposed.

48
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,090
That was just a mistake.

49
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,520
Your current identity is my family's young master.

50
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,180
Your ID card

51
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,480
must be kept by me.

52
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:34,400
Luo Xin.

53
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,480
If you really treat me as your young master,

54
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,079
then don't make decisions without authorization

55
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,210
and touch my things,

56
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,040
okay?

57
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,040
I'm sorry.

58
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,200
The banquet is about to start.

59
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:52,730
Let's go.

60
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,120
Gu Haoran.

61
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,440
The way you drifted today

62
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,930
was pretty cool.

63
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,720
I heard from the staff at the track

64
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,010
that Mr. Gu's driving skills today

65
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,800
were good enough to go to the Dragon Country Grand Prix

66
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,730
and compete for the championship.

67
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,690
That's impossible.

68
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,120
His driving skills

69
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,720
are notoriously bad.

70
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:04,760
It seems you didn't do your job well.

71
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:05,570
Lord Qianye,

72
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,960
please listen to my explanation.

73
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,960
I saw him get into the accident with my own eyes that day.

74
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,520
Even if he didn't die, he would be severely injured.

75
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,400
He couldn't be like this.

76
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,120
Shut up.

77
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,400
I don't want to hear any excuses.

78
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,770
I only want results.

79
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,530
Lord Qianye.

80
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,520
Is it possible

81
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,570
that this person...

82
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,360
he isn't Gu Haoran?

83
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,160
Now that you mention it,

84
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,680
I actually think this Gu Haoran

85
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,500
looks very much like someone.

86
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,560
Who?

87
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:39,159
A rising racing star from five years ago,

88
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:42,480
who vanished in a flash.

89
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,090
Lord Qianye.

90
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,290
Please give me another chance.

91
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,659
I must investigate this thoroughly.

92
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:55,040
You'd better not ruin my plan,

93
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,320
or else.

94
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,980
I will definitely get it done.

95
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:18,960
Luo Xin.

96
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,640
Which of these outfits suits me best?

97
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,700
They all look good.

98
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,200
Haoran has a great physique.

99
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,210
Anything looks good on him.

100
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,140
Master Haotian, you're back.

101
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,530
Brother,

102
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,250
long time no see.

103
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,960
So he is Gu Haotian.

104
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:40,610
Brother,

105
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,450
you're back.

106
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,560
Let's go outside.

107
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:52,800
Haoran,

108
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:55,280
I heard abroad that you were in a car accident.

109
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:56,210
I was so worried.

110
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,540
Now that I see you're fine,

111
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,020
I feel much more relieved.

112
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,600
Thanks for your concern.

113
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,800
During the car accident,

114
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,600
you were lucky

115
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,060
to have escaped it.

116
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,440
That bastard Ding Wen.

117
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,800
But don't worry,

118
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,280
Haoran.

119
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,440
I will definitely get revenge for you.

120
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,040
Forget it.

121
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,840
I've already got my revenge.

122
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,200
Really?

123
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,980
That's my brother.

124
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:21,400
This brother seems to care about his younger brother a lot.

125
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,680
He should be a good person.

126
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,740
By the way, Haoran.

127
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,280
When I came back from France this time,

128
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:27,560
I specially airlifted some limited-edition ice cream from there

129
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,360
for you to try.

130
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,580
Haoran.

131
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,840
This ice cream

132
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,840
should be eaten together with honey.

133
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:39,600
The taste

134
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,170
is absolutely amazing.

135
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:44,159
Try it.

136
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,240
Oh no.

137
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,780
I forgot to tell him

138
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,260
that Master Haoran is allergic to honey.

139
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:59,240
My brother has been allergic to honey since childhood.

140
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,560
If you dare to eat it,

141
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,800
it will prove you are a fake.

142
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,200
Sorry.

143
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,970
Miss Luo, it's fine.

144
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:12,680
It's fine.

145
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,000
My young master is allergic to honey.

146
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,060
You can't eat this.

147
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,799
Gu Haotian knows perfectly well that his brother is allergic to honey.

148
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,400
Why did he still give it to me?

149
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:37,360
Could it be

150
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,690
he is doubting my identity?

151
00:08:45,800 --> 00:08:46,260
Haoran.

152
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,440
My chest hurts.

153
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,240
What's wrong?

154
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,440
It's an aftereffect of the car accident.

155
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,770
I often get chest pains.

156
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,240
Should I take you to the hospital?

157
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:54,770
Brother.

158
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:55,530
I'm fine.

159
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,840
I just need some rest.

160
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,280
Luo Xin.

161
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,160
Young Master.

162
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,080
Thanks for the ice cream.

163
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,080
I'd love to eat it,

164
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,640
but I've been allergic to honey since childhood.

165
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,960
So I'll have to pass today.

166
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,560
I'm sorry.

167
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:15,900
Haoran,

168
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:16,840
eat this first.

169
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,320
Otherwise it will melt.
